name: Dondi Alentajan
text: Nakakatawa kayo. Libre na mga yung emergency service, nag-aamok kayo sa P5 ng globe. Sige, magsubscribe na lang kayo sa Lifeline na may monthly fees.    FYI, the 911 service in Davao is free. I don't know if could calling it through Globe or Smart mobile is free also. Of course through landline it's free.
